# AssetBlock Context

- Treat this repository as a .NET backend plus React/Next.js frontend codebase.
- Prefer Clean Architecture boundaries and keep business logic out of controllers/components when possible.
- Follow the existing repository-specific rules and skills first when they already cover the case.
- When a change touches both backend and frontend, keep the contract explicit and the edit set narrow.
